headline: Snap-on Incorporated to Webcast 2025 Fourth Quarter and Full Year Results Conference Call
summary: KENOSHA, Wis., January 22, 2026--Snap-on will release 2025 fourth quarter and full year results prior to the market open on February 5, 2026, with a call to follow at 10:00 a.m. ET.
